expression = re.compile(rfc._IPV4_IP_REGEX)
good_examples = ['0.0.0.0', '127.0.0.1', '250.250.250.250',
    '255.255.255.255', '249.249.249.249', '200.200.200.200',
    '199.199.199.199', '100.100.100.100']
for good_example in good_examples:
    self.assertTrue(bool(expression.fullmatch(good_example)), msg=
        "Good ipv4 address '{l}' didn't match regex".format(l=good_example))
